<br>
As you may have heard, bards can actually Mez again.  But I have a problem.  To make a long story short, bard mez was severely nerfed over a year ago, around the same time I created Chants.  Thus, I never learned how to mez.<br>
<br>
My best mez is a single target type mez, and it lasts for about 15 seconds. (lvl 53 twilight).  Given the nature of this song, what sort of advice could you give me so that I can get the most out of this song?<br>
<br>
Thanks in advance for you thoughts. <p>Chants Evensong
