<br>
With only 15 seconds on the mez, you will want to mez the creature with the most HP.<br>
<br>
This will allow your group to kill the lower HP (and thus the quickest to kill) monster first.<br>
<br>
While it is normal to mez the weaklings while the group beats on the big one first, in your case I would say do it opposite.<br>
<br>
What is the level cap on your mez by the way?<br>
<br>
Hope that helps a bit...<br>
<br>
